<a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship.html\">Canadian citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/renounce-canadian-citizenship.html\">Give up (renounce) Canadian citizenship</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwstitle section\">\n<h1 dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">\nGive up (renounce) Canadian citizenship: How to apply</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"gc-stp-stp mrgn-tp-md mrgn-tp-lg brdr-bttm\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<ul class=\"toc lst-spcd col-md-12\">\n<li class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-6\"><a class=\"list-group-item\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/renounce-canadian-citizenship.html\">1. About the process</a></li>\n<li class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-6\"><a class=\"list-group-item\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/renounce-canadian-citizenship/eligibility.html\">2. Who can apply</a></li>\n<li class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-6\"><a class=\"list-group-item active\">3. How to apply</a></li>\n<li class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-6\"><a class=\"list-group-item\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/renounce-canadian-citizenship/after-renounce-next-steps.html\">4. After you apply</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html_1343205986 mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<!-- <span data-incl-name=\"canadapost-citimmtr-eng\"></span>\n<section id=\"canadapost-citimmtr-eng-id1\">\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n\n   <p class=\"h4\">The Canada Post labour disruption will cause delays in mail delivery</p>\n    <p class=\"mrgn-tp-md\">We’re still processing applications normally. However, there will be delays in</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>sending applications mailed within or to Canada</li>\n        <li>getting mail from us</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>We encourage you to <strong>apply online if possible</strong>. If you need to apply on paper, use another courier to send us your application.</p>\n</div> \n</section> -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<h2>Choose an application package</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<p>There are 2 application packages available to you. Choose one of the following depending on your situation:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>If you’re a <strong>Canadian citizen who wants to give up citizenship</strong>, use the <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/application-forms-guides/application-renounce-canadian-citizenship-subsection-9-1.html\">Application\n      to Renounce Canadian Citizenship Under Subsection 9(1)</a>. </li>\n<li>If you <strong>automatically got citizenship</strong> because of <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/act-changes.html\">changes\n      to the Citizenship Act</a>, use the <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/application-forms-guides/application-renounce-canadian-citizenship-r7-1-amendments-citizenship-act-2009-2015.html\">Application\n      to Renounce Canadian Citizenship – R7.1</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Read the appropriate guide</strong> carefully before you complete the application form. The fee for\n  processing your application is not refundable, so make sure you are <a href=\"/services/canadian-citizenship/renounce-canadian-citizenship/eligibility.html\">eligible\n    to renounce your Canadian citizenship</a> before you apply.</p>\n<p>The application kit contains instructions. Read the instructions, and provide the required documents. If\n  information or documents are missing, your application may be delayed.</p>\n<p>If your documents are not in English or French, you must provide</p>\n<ul>\n<li>the original documents (not a photocopy) or clear and legible certified copies</li>\n<li>a translation of them in English or French and</li>\n<li>an affidavit from the translator</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Translations by family members won’t be accepted.</p>\n<h2>Apply to give up (renounce) Canadian citizenship urgently</h2>\n<p>We can process applications urgently in some situations. We will review your application to see if it qualifies. Even\n  if you qualify, we can’t guarantee your application will be processed urgently.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/renounce-canadian-citizenship/apply/urgently.html\">Apply to give up (renounce) Canadian citizenship urgently</a></p>\n<h2>Pay your application fees</h2>\n<p>In most cases, the fee to renounce your citizenship is $100.</p>\n<p>There is no fee if you <strong>automatically got your citizenship</strong> because of <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/act-changes/rules-2009-2015.html\">changes\n    to the Citizenship Act</a> and are applying under section 7.1 of the Citizenship\n  Regulations.</p>\n<p>If you’re submitting more than one application in the same envelope, you can pay all the fees together.</p>\n<p>You can <a href=\"https://www.ircc.canada.ca/english/information/fees/pay.asp\" target=\"_blank\">pay your fee online\n    (opens in a new tab)</a>. Other ways of paying your fee may be available depending on where you’re applying from.\n</p>\n<p>You can’t get a refund once we start processing your application.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<h2>Submit your application</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<p>If you <strong>live in Canada or the United States </strong>and are applying to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>renounce under <span class=\"nowrap\">subsection 9(1)</span> of the Citizenship Act</strong>, find out <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/application-forms-guides/guide-0302-application-renounce-canadian-citizenship-subsection-9-1.html#CIT0302E4\">where to send your completed application</a> form and the required documents.</li>\n<li><strong>renounce under section 7.1 of the Citizenship Regulations</strong>, find out <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/application-forms-guides/guide-0496-application-renounce-canadian-citizenship-r7-1-amendments-citizenship-act-2009-2015.html#CIT0496E6\">where to send your completed application</a> form and the required documents.<ul>\n<li>This is for people who automatically became citizens due to changes to the Citizenship Act.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you live <strong>outside Canada and outside the United States</strong>, submit your completed application form and the required documents to the <a href=\"http://travel.gc.ca/assistance/embassies-consulates?_ga=1.45225188.175555530.1427804449\">Canadian embassy, high commission or consulate</a> responsible for your area.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h3>Track your application </h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"cit-tracking-number-eng\"></span>\n<div id=\"id1\">\n<p>We recommend that you use a postal or courier service with a tracking number to ensure you get proof that your application was delivered to the IRCC office.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwspagination section\">\n<nav class=\"mrgn-bttm-lg\" role=\"navigation\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Document navigation</h2>\n<ul class=\"pager\">\n<!--<li class=\"previous\"><a href=\"index-en.html\" rel=\"prev\">Previous<span class=\"wb-inv\">: 1. [Step / section page name]</span></a></li>-->\n<li class=\"next\"><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/renounce-canadian-citizenship/after-renounce-next-steps.html\" rel=\"next\">Next: After you apply</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-8 col-md-9 col-lg-9\">\n<div class=\"wb-disable-allow\" data-ajax-replace=\"/etc/designs/canada/wet-boew/assets/feedback/page-feedback-en.html\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2025-12-15\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">About this site</h2>\n<div class=\"gc-contextual\"><div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Immigration and citizenship</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 